                  Karen Morgenroth is Manager of Information Management
                  Operations at the <%= link_to 'National Research Council
                  Canada', 'http://www.nrc-cnrc.gc.ca/' %>, where her teams
                  focus on digital information management, repositories and
                  open government initiatives.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
